Class CertificateInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.adobe.fd.signatures.pki.client.CertificateInfo
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PKIExceptionMsgIds, Serializable

    public class CertificateInfo
extends Object
implements Serializable, PKIExceptionMsgIds
    Stores certificate based information such as its revocation status and revocation info along with the associated X509Certificate.
